		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'll think about remapping the key (how about the Scroll Lock?) and indication, although I don't really get the problem with Caps LED - it is like 30 cm from the window on my PC, and I have no problem to see if it on or off without looking at it directly.
<br />
<br />'More than NROM' support is already there, but I don't plan to make animation functions, as the tool certainly wasn't designed for such things. I only had thoughts about fast switch between many nametable files, to make multiple screen edit faster.

		

		</td>
