<br />
<br />I understand why it might be easier to check caps/scroll lock mode.  I guess my biggest bother is the fact that my current mode while using your app also affects the mode of every other app I'm currently using on my computer.  I NEVER use caps lock so it's difficult to remember to turn it on and off all the time.  It become detrimental in Vi when hjkl are used to move the cursor and HJKL modify my code in undesirable ways.
<br />
<br />I'm down for holding a key while I select things similar to excel.

		

