		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think that instead of copy-pasting between buffers, when you click on the nametable with <em>apply tiles</em> enabled it should apply tiles according to the selection on the tileset. In the case you have selected only one tile, it would behave like now, but if you have selected a block (and it also could work with discrete selections) all the selected tiles are inserted at the point you click on the nametable. It would work as some kind of "brush".
<br />
<br />Does it make sense?

		

